    Merchant Video

    Our solar security camera kit gives you complete freedom. If running cables through your walls or attic doesn’t sound appealing, then don’t! No outlets near where you want to place cameras? No problem! Our wire-free cameras are solar battery-powered and are perfect for hard-to-reach areas.

    Forever Power, Solar Style, and Cost-Saving.

    Solar Powered, Non-stop Protection

    A Breeze to Install

    With solar wireless security camera system, You are free from replacing and charging the battery for good. Set the cam up and forget it.

    It takes just a few minutes to set up the camera. It’s 100% wire-free and can be placed almost anywhere. In fact, it’s so simple there’s no need to call a costly constructor.

    The power never stops with the solar security camera. Just 3 hours* of direct sunlight each day is enough to continuously power, so you never have to worry about changing the battery. And when night rolls up or a terrible weather shower strikes, the built-in battery keeps the juice flowing.

    Dual-antenna NVR provides long range WiFi range

    With dual-antenna, the camera is capable of transmitting data up to 600 feet with a clear line of sight. This gives you more power and flexibility in deciding where to position the camera. With its long-distance wireless range, you can use this camera to cover your most distant property lines.

    Take an active stance, Be Safe All the Time

    Keep uninvited guests off your premises using the motion-activated dual LED lights and siren.

    Don't Miss a Thing

    Receive real-time notifications on your phone to stay in the know when anything happens at home.

    Customize Zones

    Draw a custom activity zone to eliminate unnecessary notifications.

    Weather-resistant for year-round security

    The Camera handles almost anything Nature throws at it. It's IP 66 rating shrugs off rain and snow.

    60 Days Local Storage

    Securely store up 60 days of recordings via the 64 GB SD Card, You can also use HDD or cloud storage

    Capture clearer details and colors when it's dark

    With built-in spotlight, the wireless security cameras lights up dark area and records vivid and colorful videos like daytime. Comparing to black/white night vision mode, it provides more visual details to help you identify who is in front of door.

    Respond to Visitors, from anywhere

    Hear and speak to visitors clearly with 2-way audio right on your phone.

    Build Your Smart and Security System

    Combine all your Kittyhok products into a connected, united, and smart security solution.

    Remote viewing from your mobile with Kittyhok

    Using Kittyhok app, you can quickly view, remote control and get motion-activated push notifications

    Control It with Alexa

    Just ask Alexa to show the video of your camera on the Echo Show, and everything is done.

    Security is Our Priority

    With encrypted data technology, keep your data safe.

      I’m editing my previous review of this item.
      White solar panels were shipped with the black cameras. I waited patiently for two months to get the correct black solar panels, but all I kept hearing was “they’re not at the warehouse yet.” My home has dark brown trim and the white solar panels looked horrible. I didn’t pay a lot of money to get the exterior of my house painted so the look could be ruined by white panels. I returned them, and the restocking fee was worth every penny in aggravation.

      The idea of having a camera system that’s independent of a subscription service is genius. Setting up the main device was a little bit of a challenge but I eventually figured it out. Charging camera batteries with solar panels is brilliant. But the camera playback resolution isn’t sharp enough to identify the make/model of a vehicle or description of a person. I tried both SD and HD settings, and the results were the same.

      I replaced these cameras with Bink Outdoor, and I have no regrets.
